text: Katerina Khristoforidou (born 4 April 1984) is a Greek gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Greek female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Greece Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Thessaloniki
